Review Oh what fun it wasn’t funny Christmas photo Holiday Card – Holiday Cards Popular Oh what fun it wasn’t funny Christmas photo Holiday Card good product Oh what fun it wasn’t funny Christmas photo Holiday Card There are many featuresOh what fun it wasn’t. A funny and clever play on the "oh what fun!" jingle bells line is perfect for a tough year. Whether you’ve dealt with illness, loss or any other hardship, this simple Christmas card allows you to at least have a good sense of humor about it. It also works well for less than cooperative kids in family photo fails, crying babies with santa, defiant teens – all those not fun "nailed it" scenes. Great for family Christmas photo cards, couple Christmas cards and more. The back of the holiday card is a festive red with a dot pattern. Other styles also available. Price:$1.97
